{"tid":1036260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那賭客遭禁錮扮急病博同情 貴利衰心軟陪返內地求醫被舉報終落網","createTime":"2019-02-25T06:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T19:53:19.000Z","uid":54373,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d927337e6a5d563c4a9feb2a578e64c558c0a25","tid":1036260,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"澳門司警拘捕一名「衰好心」的中年大耳窿，懷疑有人和同黨在賭場放貸予年逾六旬債仔事主後，債仔最終輸光欠下10萬元被禁錮於酒店房還錢，但卻「詐病」博同情稱急需返內地看病，疑人見事主年邁體弱「做好心」陪伴返內地才收數，豈料卻遭人報公安及司警，被迫放棄追數潛逃。事隔半年，疑人日前再入境澳門時被司警拘捕，警方正調查其餘未落網犯罪集團成員的下落，案件有待進一步調查。（節錄）"},{"pid":"f67304450f23d48e7f02471181c6ba633a2f84b1","tid":1036260,"uid":226126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b50855c060bae9435e2e456355701c3d0c0c236","tid":1036260,"uid":74908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"夠狼死就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2801584c123225c9fb8ed3b823a7e92bba962a6c","tid":1036260,"uid":165336,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"雖然貴利係仆街，但借人錢唔撚洗還？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b46281503aed2f9f5750dbfe1212fac54750ee1","tid":1036260,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3fb467005bac600fe9f95d2b5967385bf4e947","tid":1036260,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"應該都係話帶佢睇病還三倍個d<br />\n<br />\n個大陸佬而家一定沾沾自喜"},{"pid":"e1eb785e6e38d5993b8cf454b6697c791821664e","tid":1036260,"uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"支那賭豬: D錢憑我努力借番黎, 點解要還?"},{"pid":"c39c84